               <h1>Kanye REST API</h1>
               <p>A free REST API for random Kanye West quotes (Kanye as a Service).</p>
               <h2>Usage</h2>
               <pre>
GET https://api.kanye.rest
{
  "quote": "I feel like I'm too busy writing history to read it."
}
               </pre>
               <h2>Endpoints</h2>
               <ul>
                   <li><strong>GET /</strong> - Returns a random quote.</li>
                   <li><strong>GET /text</strong> - Returns a simple text response.</li>
                   <li><strong>GET /quotes</strong> - Returns an array of quotes.</li>
               </ul>
               <h2>Warning</h2>
               <p>This response format may change.</p>
